== 9...c5 ==
Black strikes back at White's center, opening up the light-squared bishop.

This is the main branching point of the mainline Meran, since White has to choose between one of two pawn breaks: e5 and d5.

'''[[/10. e5/]]''' is the '''Old variation'''.

'''[[/10. d5/]]''' is '''Reynold's variation'''.

